# CashMate Antigravity — UI/UX Master Plan

> **Target:** UMKM Surabaya · **Stack:** Laravel 12 + Tailwind v4 + Vite 7 · **Theme:** Physics-defying financial clarity

---

## 1. Design System Foundation

### Color Palette

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--gravity-dark` | `#0a0e1a` | Base background |
| `--gravity-surface` | `#111827` | Card surfaces |
| `--gravity-glass` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.06)` | Glassmorphism panels |
| `--neon-cyan` | `#06d6a0` | Primary accent / success |
| `--neon-purple` | `#7c3aed` | Secondary accent |
| `--neon-amber` | `#f59e0b` | Warning / highlights |
| `--neon-rose` | `#f43f5e` | Expense / danger |
| `--float-white` | `#f1f5f9` | Text primary |
| `--float-muted` | `#94a3b8` | Text secondary |

### Typography
- **Primary:** `Inter` (headings + body)
- **Mono:** `JetBrains Mono` (financial figures)

### Shape & Motion
- Border radius: `12px` (cards), `9999px` (pills)
- Glassmorphism: `backdrop-blur(16px)` + `border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`
- Float animation: `translateY` oscillation 8px over 3s ease-in-out
- Particle system: Canvas-based, 30-60 FPS target

