## 6. Animation Specification

| Animation | Trigger | CSS/JS | Duration |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Float Idle** | Page load | CSS `@keyframes float` | 3s infinite |
| **Particle Field** | Background always-on | Canvas API | 60fps |
| **Gravity Pull** | File drop on zone | JS `requestAnimationFrame` | 800ms |
| **Data Fly-Out** | OCR extraction complete | CSS `transform` + JS stagger | 1.2s |
| **Ball Physics** | Category assignment | Canvas / CSS spring | 600ms |
| **Chart Bounce** | Touch/hover on chart bar | CSS `scale` + `transition` | 300ms |
| **Report Slide** | Download triggered | CSS `translateY` + `opacity` | 1s |
| **Glass Shimmer** | Card hover | CSS `background-position` | 400ms |

